sequenceDiagram
  participant M as CP Master BDMA
  participant TOP as TOP regs
  participant H as HCQD
  participant IB as Interaction Buffer
  participant U as CP User cmd_entry

  M->>TOP: write MCQD_ADDR_LO/HI
  M->>TOP: write BINDDMA_HCQDID
  TOP->>H: bind MCQD to HCQD
  H->>IB: expose candidate bit / packet fifo
  U->>IB: ib_get_candidate_bitmask
  U->>IB: ib_peek_packet
  U->>U: cmd_handle_packet
